{"tid":439053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發 羅哲斯被港拒入境 英國傳召中國大使","createTime":"2017-10-17T12:57:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-17T15:44:53.000Z","uid":41404,"like":39,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"fefe14b954be81fb5aadf982c51638a54e0caa1a","tid":439053,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T12:57:23.000Z","msg":"國保守黨人權委員會副主席羅哲斯（Benedict Rogers）早前被拒入境香港，英國外交部國務大臣田銘祺（Mark Field）於下議院會議上回應議員質詢，重申外交部非常關注事件，又批評羅哲斯被拒入境是漠視一國兩制，已就此事傳召中國駐英大使。<br />\n<br />\n英國保守黨人權委員會主席Fiona Bruce昨日在下議院會議上指出，銅鑼灣書店股東及店長等五人「被失蹤」、民選議員被判入獄，以及羅哲斯被拒入境，反映本港的一國兩制持續被侵蝕，質詢英國外交部有何行動。田銘祺回應，英國與香港的關係仍然緊密，外交部非常關注羅哲斯被拒入境，認為此舉「絕對漠視一國兩制（absolute disregard of the &quot;One Country, Two Systems&quot; principle）」。他指，外交部已在近日傳召中國駐英大使。下議院議長貝爾考（John Bercow）亦指羅哲斯的待遇「可恥（scandalous）」。"},{"pid":"b3204bb8d0c0d5a504629e3ad064642aba8317df","tid":439053,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T12:59:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171017/57344512\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171017%2F57344512&d=9%2BKa5FAbaOf5Ob%2F8Y%2FQE9ywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=1a561fbc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171017%2F57344512&h=a5f3108d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171017/57344512</a>"},{"pid":"72fa109bf9c44d473988ffa32af74575d4509c32","tid":439053,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T13:02:00.000Z","msg":"外交部國務大臣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"385c3cc2d01dcf6b06acf0c5f1cc40326b6d4a35","tid":439053,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T13:02:58.000Z","msg":"別干預別國內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb43e80860821ef1f6376f6ba71728753d164dc","tid":439053,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dis